@startuml
title Séquence métier — Relancer les remboursements (admin)
' ------------------------------------------------------------------
' Style impression A4 (PFE FSEG) — lisibilité : polices ~11–12 pt visibles,
' DPI 240, retour à la ligne des messages. Inclure juste après la ligne title.
' Export PNG pour Word/LaTeX : viser largeur <= zone utile A4 (~17 cm).
' ------------------------------------------------------------------
scale max 1550 width
skinparam dpi 240
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam HyperlinkUnderline false

skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam titleFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam arrowThickness 1.25
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam NoteFontSize 10
skinparam LegendFontSize 10
skinparam footerFontSize 10
skinparam headerFontSize 10

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 14
skinparam BoxPadding 8
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #444444
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ArrowColor #222222
skinparam ActorBorderColor #222222
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #333333
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam EntityBackgroundColor #F8FFF8
skinparam ControlBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
skinparam BoundaryBackgroundColor #F5F5FF
actor Admin as admin
boundary "Administration (ops)" as UI
control "Contrôleur" as Svc
entity "Base de données" as DB
participant "PasserellePaiement (mock)" as PG

admin -> UI: Consulter les remboursements en echec
UI -> Svc: GET /api/admin/ops/failed-refunds?resolved=false&limit=...
Svc -> DB: FailedRefundEvent.find({ resolved: false }) tri date
DB --> Svc: failedRefunds[]
Svc --> UI: 200 { failedRefunds }
UI --> admin: Affichage liste

admin -> UI: Declencher une relance (lot)
UI -> Svc: POST /api/admin/ops/retry-refunds { limit? }
note right of Svc
  **Code :** `adminOpsService.retryRefundsOnce` appelle `cronService.retryFailedRefunds`.
  Parcours des evenements non resolus (limite), pour chacun : charge Transaction + Investment,
  appelle `mockProvider.refundPayment(...)`, met a jour statuts ou incremente retryCount sur l'event.
end note

Svc -> DB: Charger FailedRefundEvent (resolved=false, limite)
DB --> Svc: events

loop pour chaque event
  Svc -> DB: Charger Transaction (dernier attempt) + Investment
  DB --> Svc: tx, inv
  alt tx ou inv introuvable
    Svc -> DB: Marquer l'event resolu (orphelin)
  else
    Svc -> PG: refundPayment(provider, providerPaymentId, amount, reason)
    PG --> Svc: { ok: true/false }
    alt remboursement OK (provider)
      Svc -> DB: Transaction REFUNDED / refundStatus SUCCEEDED, Investment REFUNDED, event resolu
    else echec provider
      Svc -> DB: FailedRefundEvent.retryCount++, error mis a jour
    end
  end
end

Svc --> UI: 200 { ok: true, summary: { scanned, succeeded, failed } }
UI --> admin: Resultat agrege

@enduml
